## Como iniciar
Chame esse fluxo alterando essa URL abaixo
```
https://webhook.domino.com/webhook/agents?connection={{ conexao }}&company={{ id da empresa no directus }}
```
Na pratica ela ficara assim quando substituido as informacoes: 

## Chatwoot
```
https://flows.nexus.bitfy.ai/webhook/agents?connection=chatwoot&company=b17a26f7-525e-47d4-950d-9a6a7b298dc8
```

## Evolution
```
https://flows.nexus.bitfy.ai/webhook/agents?connection=evolution&company=b17a26f7-525e-47d4-950d-9a6a7b298dc8
```

=SELECT 
    i.service, i.address, i.token
FROM companies_integrations cpin
JOIN integrations i 
  ON cpin.integrations_id = i.id
WHERE cpin.companies_id = '{{ $('A:Recebe dados conexao').item.json.query.company }}'
